HEADWORD: Clawback
<hw>Claw"back`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A flatterer or
sycophant.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Take heed of these
<xex>clawbacks</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Latimer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
