==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Clawback
<hw>Claw"back`</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Flattering; sycophantic.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Like a <qex>clawback</qex> parasite.</q> <rj><qau>Bp.
